{"tid":2047553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"雙十一槍擊案 手足獲准繼續保釋","createTime":"2020-06-02T07:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T13:03:21.000Z","uid":37971,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85b04b9b8b05def1a3ce0e652a9a4bf217dce60d","tid":2047553,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"#西九龍裁判法院第三庭<br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#1111西灣河<br />\n<br />\n👤D1周（21）<br />\n👤D2胡（19）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員：故意阻正當執勤的警員A (D1, D2)<br />\n(2) 企圖搶劫罪：搶A的槍 (D1, D2)<br />\n(3) 企圖從合法羈押逃脫罪：D1（中槍後）企圖在A的合法羈押下逃走 (D1)<br />\n<br />\n控方反對繼續保釋，要求收押二人<br />\n<br />\n✅裁判官准許二人繼續保釋✅<br />\n擔保條件如下：<br />\n- $3000擔保金<br />\n- 家長人事擔保$5000<br />\n- 不得離港<br />\n- 須交出所有旅遊證件<br />\n- 宵禁11pm-7am<br />\n- 每周到警署報到2次<br />\n- 須居住在報稱住址，如更改住址須24小時前通知警方<br />\n<br />\n押後至 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年6月30日 上午930</span></strong> 再訊。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F5584&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=487ca834\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5584</a><br />\n<br />\n721 唔見人<br />\n831 打死人<br />\n101 槍殺人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>雙十一 狂殺人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dd418dfbc95ead66ba1c3bfd6a9f056bb598a4c5","tid":2047553,"uid":199893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"警員A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出晒名啦<br />\n佢嗰兩個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1000592d0152ae14d6bf9bdb2d891584a8ed29ed","tid":2047553,"uid":37971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"一日未撤銷控罪<br />\n一日都未可以慶祝<